metadata.name: Stone Tunnel
metadata.description:
It is one of the tunnels that fascinate people with its stone road tunnels, curves, sharp cliffs and natural beauties in winter, built in 132 years with the hard struggle of the local people and the support of the state in the Kemaliye district of Erzincan.


Artis: Mürsel TAHTACI
Camera:Fujifilm XT-2 
Dimensions: 6000×4000
Resolution: 300dpi
Location: Kemaliye –Erzincan / Türkiye
Date: 26.01.2022
Edition: 1/1
